'''Drebbin''' were horned creatures native to [[Dathomir/Legends|Dathomir]]. In [[8 ABY/Legends|8 ABY]], [[Teneniel Djo]] said to [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] that they preyed on [[Rancor/Legends|rancors]], though subsequent [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] sources described them as quarry for the rancor.

A major predator on the world, the drebbin had thick hides and evoked fear among the other [[Species/Legends|species]] of Dathomir. In [[Gender/Legends|her]] manifesto ''[[Wild Power]]'', [[Mother (title)/Legends|Mother]] [[Talzin/Legends|Talzin]] of the [[Dathomirian/Legends|Dathomirian]] [[Nightsisters/Legends|Nightsisters]] likened that [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force-using]] sect to the drebbin in their shared disregard for those they saw as inferior.<ref name="Sith">''[[Book of Sith: Secrets from the Dark Side]]''</ref>

